            <title>[SPARK-28556] Error should also be sent to QueryExecutionListener.onFailure</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-28556</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Right now Error is not sent to&#160;QueryExecutionListener.onFailure. If there is any Error when running a query,&#160;QueryExecutionListener.onFailure cannot be triggered.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
